        <div class='col-md-12'>
            <div class='card'>
                <div class='card-header'>
                    <h1>Events</h1>
                </div>
                <div class='card-body'>
                  <p>The Events Page shows all SUITS events and allows users to Log Attendance for open events. </p>
                  <%= image_tag "EventsUserIndex.png", class:'card-img-top' %>
                    <h3>Ordering</h3>
                    <p>To sort the events click one of the blue arrows(as seen above)
                       to sort by that column (ascending or descending depending on the arrow). </p>
                    <h3>Logging Attendance</h3>
                    <p>To log your attendance click the Log Attendance button Next to an event (only works when the event is open). </p>
                    <%= image_tag "Log User Attendance.png", class:'card-img-top' %>
                    <p>To log attendance simply enter the password for the event and click submit attendance as seen above. </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% if !current_user.gen_member? %>
        <div class='col-md-12'>
            <div class='card'>
                <div class='card-header'>
                    <h1>Admin Events</h1>
                </div>
                <div class='card-body'>
                    <h3>Adminâ€™s Features</h3>
                      <%= image_tag "AdminEventView.png", class:'card-img-top' %>
                      <h3>Adding a New Event</h3>
                      <p>To add a new event simply click Add New Event as seen above and then fill out the event form as seen
                         below. Once you click submit event the event will be added. </p>
                      <%= image_tag "CreateEvent.PNG", class:'card-img-top' %>
                      <h3>Adding Attendances/Deleting Attendances(from events)</h3>
                      <p>This is the Attendances view for events. Here you can see the names and emails of everyone who has
                         attended an event. Here you can delete attendance if you choose to do so.</p>
                      <%= image_tag "EventAttendances.png", class:'card-img-top' %>
                      <p>You may also add an attendance for an event by clicking the Add Attendance for this Event link. You then can
                         click Log Attendance for the specific user and the attendance will be added.  </p>
                        <%= image_tag "LogAttendance.PNG", class:'card-img-top' %>
                         <h3>Editing an Event</h3>
                         <p>To edit an event click edit on the Events page and then make any changes necessary to the form and the event will be updated with them.</p>
                         <h3>Deleting an event</h3>
                         <p>To delete an event click Delete on the Events page and then confirm your Deletion. </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% end %>

